      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Liverpool's Victorian housing stock is particularly vulnerable to frozen pipes in winter. Most burst pipe emergencies are preventable with simple preparation. Here is your complete guide.</p>
